  <brief_title>An Investigation of Light Therapy for Cancer-related Fatigue (The LITE Study)</brief_title>
  <acronym>LITE</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Trial of Light Therapy on Biomarkers, Sleep/Wake Activity, and Quality of Life in Individuals With Post-treatment Cancer-related Fatigue</official_title>
